OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FFormer children's commissioner
OL,7,FBaroness Anne Longfield will chair the
OL,8,Fnational grooming gangs inquiry, the
OL,9,Fhome secretary has announced.
OL,11,FThe long-awaited announcement comes
OL,12,Falmost six months after the government
OL,13,Ffirst announced the inquiry, which has
OL,14,Falso been blighted by rows about its
OL,15,Fscope.
OL,17,FThe former children's commissioner
OL,18,Fserved in the role from 2015-2021, and
OL,19,Flast year founded the Centre for Young
OL,20,FLives think tank aimed at improving
OL,21,Fthe lives of children and families.
