OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FShe was made a Labour peer for her
OL,7,Fwork devoted to children's rights
OL,8,Fearlier this year, and she will step
OL,9,Fdown from the party as she carries out
OL,10,Fthe inquiry's work, Home Secretary
OL,11,FShabana Mahmood said.
OL,13,FMahmood also confirmed the proposed
OL,14,Fterms of reference for the inquiry,
OL,15,Finsisting it will be "time-limited"
OL,16,Fand completed within three years with
OL,17,F#65 million in funding.
