OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FThe scope of the inquiry will be fully
OL,7,Fconfirmed by March after consultation
OL,8,Fwith survivors and experts, when it
OL,9,Fwill then "begin its work in earnest."
OL,11,FThe home secretary told MPs - "I know
OL,12,Fthat for many, this day is long
OL,13,Foverdue", and insisted "what is
OL,14,Frequired now is a moment of reckoning,
OL,15,Fwe must cast fresh light on this
OL,16,Fdarkness."
OL,18,FBaroness Longfield said the inquiry
OL,19,F"will not shy away from difficult or
OL,20,Funcomfortable truths wherever we find
OL,21,Fthem".
