OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FShe added: "The scourge of grooming
OL,7,Fgangs has not been adequately tackled
OL,8,Fover the past decades.
OL,10,F"That must change, and I will do
OL,11,Feverything in my power to make this
OL,12,Fhappen."
OL,14,FThe first thing the chair and
OL,15,Fpanelists will do is meet with victims
OL,16,Flater this week, Mahmood told MPs.
