OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FShe also announced she had
OL,7,Fcommissioned new research to help with
OL,8,Fthe "understanding of perpetrators'
OL,9,Fbackgrounds and motivations, including
OL,10,Ftheir ethnicity and religion."
OL,12,FThe government will bring in a legal
OL,13,Fduty for information sharing between
OL,14,Fsafeguarding partners, a "unique
OL,15,Fidentifier for each child linking all
OL,16,Fdata across government", and upgrade
OL,17,Fpolicy technology to help with data
OL,18,Fsharing.
