OL,6,FNo area will be able to "resist" a
OL,7,Flocal investigation into grooming
OL,8,Fgangs, Mahmood said, confirming Oldham
OL,9,Fwill have a local investigation and
OL,10,Fthat other sites will be identified in
OL,11,Fdue course.
OL,13,FThe home secretary also announced two
OL,14,Fother panelists to work alongside
OL,15,FBaroness Longfield, leading the
OL,16,Finquiry.
