OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FResponding to the announcement, Shadow
OL,7,FHome Secretary Chris Philp said it
OL,8,Fshould not have taken six months to
OL,9,Ffind a chair, and called for an
OL,10,Fapology from the PM for "disgracefully
OL,11,Fsmearing those calling for an inquiry
OL,12,Fas "far right'".
OL,14,FMahmood said it was now time to
OL,15,F"elevate this discussion beyond our
OL,16,Fusual trade-offs of party politics
OL,17,Facross this despatch box" and to do
OL,18,Fthe right thing for the victims.
