OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FThe government announced the statutory
OL,7,Finquiry into the grooming gangs
OL,8,Fscandal in June this year after months
OL,9,Fof pressure from opposition parties
OL,10,Fand many survivors to implement a full
OL,11,Fnational probe.
OL,13,FAs part of a review into the grooming
OL,14,Fgangs scandal led by Baroness Louise
OL,15,FCasey, it was recommended that the
OL,16,Fgovernment launch a national inquiry.
OL,18,FBut many have criticised the slow
OL,19,Fprogress in getting the inquiry off
OL,20,Fthe ground, particularly after issues
OL,21,Faround the choice of chair.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
