OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, Casey wrote to survivors
OL,7,Fto let them know that the new chair
OL,8,Fwould be announced, insisting "I
OL,9,Fremain very much committed to the
OL,10,Festablishment of the inquiry alongside
OL,11,Fthe new police investigation and other
OL,12,Frecommendations following on from my
OL,13,Faudit."
OL,15,FShe also said she had spoken
OL,16,Findividually to the chair and all the
OL,17,Fpanelists about "not shrinking away
OL,18,Ffrom telling uncomfortable truths."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
