OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FFormer police officer Jim Gamble
OL,7,Fwithdrew from the process in October,
OL,8,Fsaying he did not feel he had a
OL,9,F"consensus of trust" among the
OL,10,Fsurvivors' group on account of his
OL,11,Fprevious profession.
OL,13,FHe also pointed to a "toxic
OL,14,Fenvironment" surrounding the chair's
OL,15,Fselection, and "political opportunism
OL,16,Fand point-scoring," calling it out as
OL,17,Fregrettable given the severity of the
OL,18,Finquiry's purpose.
