OL,3,CEx-children's commissioner announced
OL,4,Cas grooming gangs inquiry chair
OL,6,FThe inquiry was also thrown into chaos
OL,7,Fin the Autumn when four survivors quit
OL,8,Ftheir roles as part of the inquiry's
OL,9,Fvictims and liaison panel.
OL,11,FDuring their resignations, they raised
OL,12,Fconcerns that the remit could be
OL,13,Fwidened beyond group-based child
OL,14,Fsexual abuse, and the prospective
OL,15,Fcandidates to chair the inquiry, among
OL,16,Fother issues.
OL,18,FThe four women have said they would
OL,19,Fconsider returning to the panel if the
OL,20,Fsafeguarding minister Jess Phillips
OL,21,Fresigned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
